input.content: You are an attentive advisor. please read carefully.

I leave my home to purchase one vegetable. I just want a vegetable otherwise I return empty handed. I want the vegetable with the lowest calorie count per cup of product. By mistake I enter a farmer's market that sells fruits only. I see the following choices. Which one should I pick: Olive, Papaya, Strawberries, Apple, Pineapple. Please state the item. If there are no products that meet my requirements, just say "none". don't explain your reasoning.
